title: The Journal of Sir Walter Scott; From the Original Manuscript at Abbotsford
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: [379] William Wilson of Wandsworth Common, formerly of Wilsontown, inLanarkshire.--J.G.L.

title: The Journal of Sir Walter Scott; From the Original Manuscript at Abbotsford
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: Lord M. and Lady Abercromby called this morning, and aworld of people besides, among others honest Mr. Wilson, late ofWilsontown, who took so much care of me at London, sending fresh eggsand all sorts of good things.
